<mvc:View controllerName="sap.ui.demo.todo.controller.App" xmlns="sap.m" xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" xmlns:tnt="sap.tnt" displayBlock="true" height="94%">
	<tnt:ToolHeader>
		<Image id="appLogo" src="./img/nic-pad-logo.png" />
		<Title id="appTitle" text="{i18n>appTitle}" />
		<ToolbarSpacer id="tbarSpacer" />
		<Button id="buttonVersion" visible="{appView>/enableMenu}" text="v0.1.0" type="Transparent" press=".onVersionPress" tooltip="{i18n>ttVersion}" />
		<Button id="buttonHelp" visible="{appView>/enableMenu}" icon="sap-icon://sys-help" type="Transparent" press=".onHelpPress" tooltip="{i18n>ttHelp}" />
		<Button id="buttonUser" visible="{appView>/enableMenu}" type="Transparent" icon="sap-icon://employee" press=".handlePressUserMenu" tooltip="{i18n>ttUserMenu}" />
	</tnt:ToolHeader>
	<Shell appWidthLimited="false">
		<App id="app" />
	</Shell>
</mvc:View>